481
00:35:25,199 --> 00:35:26,559
[SPEAKER_01] I možete učiniti više stvari.

482
00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:30,639
[SPEAKER_01] I to je, ima dvije velike faze u tome da netko nešto gradi.

483
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:32,960
