554
00:40:05,199 --> 00:40:10,239
[SPEAKER_02] Ponekad je život, ako nemate izbora, malo lakši jer se ne morate brinuti o tome.

555
00:40:10,639 --> 00:40:11,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, da, možete to uzeti svaki dan.

